### Academic Year API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Get all academic years
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academic-years
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get active academic year
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academic-years/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get academic year by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/academic-years/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Create new academic year
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/academic-years
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Academic Year 2024-2025",
  "startDate": "2024-09-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2025-08-31T23:59:59Z",
  "isActive": true
}

### 5. Update academic year
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/academic-years/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Academic Year 2024-2025 (Updated)",
  "startDate": "2024-09-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2025-08-31T23:59:59Z",
  "isActive": true
}

### 6. Delete academic year
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/academic-years/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
